One day, after visiting the night market, I didn’t know what to eat. I opened Google MAP and searched for nearby food. I have eaten a lot of hidden food in the corner, but from I never thought that a hot pot restaurant could be opened in such a secret place!

The store is very small, there are only three tables in it, when it is full, the boss asked us to wait a moment, watching the full of seats, made me more curious about this mysterious shop.

After I took a seat, I looked at the menu. There are many kinds of soup and meat, and the price is not much different from that of ordinary しゃぶしゃぶ, but the desserts and drinks are also homemade. It seems that the amount of work preparation is really not light.

A plate full of large grass prawns, large clams, and scallops, the freshness is amazing, it is really sweet and delicious.
